{"tid":124554,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「官打民不羞，父打子不羞」百年前魯迅痛筆 今天落在香港身上","createTime":"2017-02-17T16:34:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T14:10:18.000Z","uid":41954,"like":88,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9dbf523bf5a495d97c9e67ca7ee09f999c356b0c","tid":124554,"uid":41954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T16:34:33.000Z","msg":"百年前，魯迅評中國人自古以來有一種<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「官打民不羞，父打子不羞 」</strong></span>的心態；百年後，在回歸十七年的香港警隊身上，糾纏於中國人的陰影，卻再一次在回歸後的香港鮮活起來。<br />\n<br />\n在古代中國，「官」的意義就和父母一樣，故平民會稱地方執法者為「父母官」，<strong>打平民如教子，殺刁民如棄子，國的官打民甚至殺民，與家的父打子甚至棄子，在<strong>「國與家」</strong>之下，都是合情、合理、合法的。</strong>所以前警務處長曾偉雄，有一次在傳媒質問詢警察毆打示威學生與市民，留下了一句令港人譁然且廣為傳誦的明言：<strong>「警方就像慈母保護孩子一樣。」</strong>在眾多傳媒的攝錄機下，警員手起棍落打得市民頭破血流的事實，在一哥眼中竟成了「慈母保護子女」一般，令旁人側目、譁然。然而，此番言論在警隊上下卻獲得掌聲和讚同，更堅定了「慈母、慈父們」對市民使用武力的信心。<br />\n<br />\n此等荒唐事，在普通市民與學生眼中似乎難以理解，為甚麼暴力的傷害、攻擊場面，在警察和一眾支持警方者的眼中，會成了「慈母」保護市民的英勇故事，而且對此深信不疑？抱著這樣的迷惑，卻想起魯迅那深刻的筆觸。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">原來百年來，有些東西一直沒有改變。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n十七年前，前警務處長李明逵就在政府總部外，警察揮拳打向示威者一事作出回應：<strong>「是沒有情形下，警察可以揮拳打人。」</strong>其實，警察在執勤期間對犯人或疑犯甚至市民施加武力，已經不是甚麼公開的秘密。不過，在2000年時，香港回歸不過三年，警民關係尚算良好，警隊備受一般市民尊重，兒童也會視「警察叔叔」為正義的化身。<strong>香港警察即使在警署內如何對犯人或被捕疑犯，施加拳打腳踢、鎚仔&amp;#25596;心口的招式，在公眾場合面對市民時，對此等公開秘密依然會避忌三分，警察對平民濫用私刑雖然常見，但知道此等行為不能浮上水面，</strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>所以警員對同袍在公開場合，因不慎施展平日在警署的慣用招式被拘捕和起訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，會視為不幸但合理，縱使心底下同情該名同袍，也不會明目張膽的支持「犯罪行為」，</strong></span>故此前警務處長面對傳媒的時候，並不需顧慮警隊上下的立場，說出與現今警務處長盧偉聰截然不同，但作為一支為民眾服務的專業警隊應該要說的講法。"},{"pid":"7529fbcb834b0e38560748aa0e6d67b68d13a5a4","tid":124554,"uid":41954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T16:36:36.000Z","msg":"今天，七警案塵埃落定，然而警隊上下卻對此深感不忿，<span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong>甚至有現職警員公然在社交網絡辱罵主審法官為「狗官」</strong></span>，一哥的聲明沒半點譴責犯罪警員之意，更聲言會照顧好其親屬，有網民諷刺其言論彷彿有如舊香港社團橫行時代，社團大佬對因事入獄成員之口吻一般，與過往對警員犯罪的口徑大相逕庭。盧偉聰此舉亦彷彿暗示(或明示)警隊上下對法庭的判決不服，警務人員協會更聲然考慮組織警員上街抗議。<br />\n<br />\n如此明顯且嚴重的犯罪行為，為甚麼在警隊上下會將其合理化且公然挑戰司法機關？<strong>在種種的片段，過往兩任警務處長發言、警隊文化、警隊上下對判決的反應，與魯迅百年前深刻的筆觸連繫起來，答案馬上豁然開朗。<span style=\"color: purple;\">應變的，沒有改變；不應改變的，卻改變了</span>。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>警隊近年有一種畸形文化，自警隊過去數十年的文化之中被孕育出來，</strong></span>過往存在沉於&amp;#26545;底的私刑文化，如今理所當然的浮出水面　&mdash;　<strong>今天的香港警方，視私刑毆打市民為其合理的「特權」，視司法機關的判決是對其「應有權利」的剝奪，在魯迅勁筆下的「官打民不羞，父打子不羞 」 ，</strong>今天在香港警隊身上完美「體現」。因為香港警隊上下，對毆打示威者的行為，視之如同「父母」管教子女一般，<span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong>穿上警服</strong>，<strong>他就是官，你就是民</strong></span>，今天用棍打得你頭破血流，<strong>是「慈父慈母」管教迷途犯事孩童的方法</strong>，今天法庭判決他們的行為違法，警隊上下無不恨得咬牙切齒，為甚麼他們執行職務，扮演「父母」管教「頑劣子女」的一幕，會落得兩年牢獄生涯的下場？<strong>至此，前警務處長曾偉雄為何會評揮棒痛毆市民的警員為「慈母」的荒唐言論，終於在百年前的中國人身上，找到答案。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「官打民不羞，父打子不羞 」 ，百年前覆蓋在中國人身上的陰影，今天卻將香港遮蓋。"},{"pid":"5dd5ee923f3f0fb2ac0ae3ead4bd893fa81c3617","tid":124554,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T16:43:28.000Z","msg":"反映中國人過左100年都係無進步過，仲要拖埋人落水<br />\n即使比多100年都係一9樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日有班人講「比d 時間比中國人啦一定會變好」 可以收哂佢地皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"229dce14c8e45042179f82b96c36770934cc643b","tid":124554,"uid":41954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T16:46:46.000Z","msg":"打錯字　名言　先岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2f23c1402a9a39d8c0f245aef282e6b0273a47a","tid":124554,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T16:49:53.000Z","msg":"好文好文！"},{"pid":"7c393251931051c6e09e0dca7a7078ee6f60baae","tid":124554,"uid":43510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T16:50:23.000Z","msg":"句野出處？"},{"pid":"8563abcd3402c02e9a321c228a92a3821c532041","tid":124554,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T16:52:15.000Z","msg":"你寫架?唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"943e6937f81f472d7bae28e5799d973607a40dae","tid":124554,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T16:54:44.000Z","msg":"俾D廢老睇啱晒"},{"pid":"dfd324f58696e9b33afed44d2a8233806c3cf266","tid":124554,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T17:01:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>俾D廢老睇啱晒</blockquote><br />\n咪屌返你轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n由尻佢地啦，都就死"},{"pid":"4976f973fa0f800cfd25086b20132c796541ca42","tid":124554,"uid":3342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T17:06:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"007fc9db3c53cdb841972b8bef2f4f9dec7407cb","tid":124554,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T17:10:30.000Z","msg":"寫得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9c5b24d9776b1f2a9bb59cdfc25e66111c31862","tid":124554,"uid":41954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T17:12:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>句野出處？</blockquote><br />\n中國古諺 <br />\n我用呢句黎概括魯迅對中國人奴性既批評姐"},{"pid":"cc5d55f7f012085443dbabed3d77338802a86759","tid":124554,"uid":44184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T17:17:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1a9539e48dce5e3b33e0beb9755235ef14938b3","tid":124554,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T17:18:16.000Z","msg":"邊個寫既 樓主寫既?"},{"pid":"f51f57e64d68fa4efbe805861130e1bc805b4b69","tid":124554,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T17:20:44.000Z","msg":"支那垃圾文化"},{"pid":"b50679108a26ba9dcc165d7d5ac88be02e73e443","tid":124554,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T17:21:26.000Z","msg":"不錯"},{"pid":"6fc6b13d5755bb78e3bd5d405d21a6d44a3260f1","tid":124554,"uid":59693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T17:23:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fd5d88019ba5455ef578d3d3cd6ab7957850d5a","tid":124554,"uid":41954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T17:41:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e38f00fa80f9382795b9a3f599eced29844be4a8","tid":124554,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T17:49:08.000Z","msg":"Sauce? Original?"},{"pid":"73eef8195a482ef12f322fb009039d654e1c1ed3","tid":124554,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T17:54:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好文"},{"pid":"cdd4e6f8217f80df61a7bc7658fa9b41aee6e389","tid":124554,"uid":41954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T18:01:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Sauce? Original?</blockquote><br />\n我驚講出黎<br />\n會比人告我有犯罪意或不誠實使用電腦沒收我notebook<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3c06dbbceca323152bae3dfcdd2734897801424","tid":124554,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T18:19:50.000Z","msg":"好！"},{"pid":"cab89ce391f771c826e436c80381f079680f4294","tid":124554,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T18:25:38.000Z","msg":"劣根性"},{"pid":"a9f3ba3cec1e0d19376af62dbda93382599de8a1","tid":124554,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T18:28:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/-_fR45YqKDlM/UeyVxhK-kYI/AAAAAAAAa4c/kk2lTYHCqdk/w506-h750/%25E9%25B2%2581%25E8%25BF%2585%25EF%25BC%259A%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259B%25BD%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25BE%2588%25E5%25AE%25B9%25E6%2598%2593%25E5%258F%2598%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%25A5%25B4%25E9%259A%25B6%25E7%259A%2584.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh5.googleusercontent.com%2F-_fR45YqKDlM%2FUeyVxhK-kYI%2FA